                 Prefix Verb   URI Pattern                                     Controller#Action

  edit_user_registration GET    /users/edit(.:format)                           my_devise/registrations#edit
                         PATCH  /users(.:format)                                my_devise/registrations#update
                         PUT    /users(.:format)                                my_devise/registrations#update
                         DELETE /users(.:format)                                my_devise/registrations#destroy

               edit_user GET    /users/:id/edit(.:format)                       users#edit

